  "title": "Admin & Operation Support (Insurance Industry) (12 Months Contract) #NKC",
  "description": "<p><p>Process operational tasks accurately and within stipulated timelines in accordance with standard procedures.</p></p><p><p>Perform data entry, data checking, and document verification to ensure accuracy and completeness.</p></p><p><p>Manage document scanning, indexing, uploading, and archival in the appropriate system folders.</p></p><p><p>Prepare, update, and maintain periodic operational and data reports (daily/weekly/monthly).</p></p><p><p>Ensure all information and reports are accurate before submission to relevant stakeholders.</p></p><p><p>Support system enhancements and participate in user testing activities when required.</p></p><p><p>Liaise with internal and external stakeholders to ensure smooth operations and timely communication.</p></p><p><p>Handle ad-hoc administrative tasks and respond to enquiries as assigned<br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /><br /><br />Interested applicants may email resume to kellychooi@recruitexpress.com.sg</p><p>Chooi Kelly (CEI Registration No: R25136207)</p><p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd (EA: 99C4599)</p><p></p><p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted</p><p></p><p></p></p>",
